Before purchasing, be sure to check the size chart for a perfect fit.In conclusion, the COOFANDY Sleeveless Beach Shirt for Men is a must-have for anyone looking to stay comfortable and stylish during the summer months. Its versatility, thoughtful design, and easy care make it a valuable addition to your wardrobe. Highly recommended!

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not as stretchy as the description states. Order up a size!!
reviews.reviewText: This shirt came neatly folded in a sealed plastic bag. It had the label tucked into the collar area. When I unfolded it, I noticed the material did not have any give. It was a cool, silky material, polyester. The color was true to the color listed. It fit snug in the chest area and arm/sleeve area. I would order up a size. It is not comfortable when you order true to size.I like the concept of this shirt and the design. Once again, order up a size or you can't wear it. I would order again if I went up in size...again that seemed to be the biggest issue!
